Spesifikasi :
** Processor : Intel® Core™ Ultra 7 155H, 16C (6P + 8E + 2LPE) / 22T, Max Turbo up to 4.8GHz, 24MB

** Memory : 32GB Soldered LPDDR5x-7467
** Storage : 1TB SSD M.2 2242 PCIe® 4.0x4 NVMe®
** Display : 14" 4K (3840x2400) OLED 400nits Glossy / Anti-fingerprint, 100% DCI-P3, 60Hz, Eyesafe®, Dolby® Vision™, DisplayHDR™ 500, Glass, Touch
** OS : Windows® 11 Home + Office Home & Student 2021
** Network : Wi-Fi® 6E, 11ax 2x2 + BT5.3

** Ports :
1x USB-A (USB 10Gbps / USB 3.2 Gen 2), Always On
1x USB-C® (USB 10Gbps / USB 3.2 Gen 2), with USB PD 3.0 and DisplayPort™ 1.4
2x USB-C® (Thunderbolt™ 4 / USB4® 40Gbps), with USB PD 3.0 and DisplayPort™ 1.4
1x Headphone / microphone combo jack (3.5mm)

** Keyboard : Backlit, English
** Speakers : 4 stereo speakers, 2W x2 (woofers on the side), 2W x2 (front-facing tweeters on hinge bar), optimized with Dolby® Atmos®, Smart Amplifier (AMP), audio by Bowers & Wilkins
** Camera : 5.0MP + IR with Privacy Shutter
** Battery : Integrated 75Wh
** Adapter : 65W USB-C® (3-pin)
